    "text": "Actually I think we can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.57,
    "endTime": 111.53999999999999,
    "text": "Does anyone remember what we were doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.54,
    "endTime": 114.82000000000001,
    "text": "I feel like we were supposed to be doing something..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.24,
    "endTime": 117.03999999999999,
    "text": "But now I can't remember!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.04,
    "endTime": 119.66000000000001,
    "text": "Oh man what happened here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.94,
    "endTime": 120.8,
    "text": "Oh dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.08,
    "endTime": 123.86,
    "text": "Probably should have obliviated after we fixed everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.18,
    "endTime": 125.74000000000001,
    "text": "Great idea, Newt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.3,
